---
import { homeFaqs, productInfo, siteConfig } from '../data/site';

const shareUrl = encodeURIComponent(siteConfig.url + '/');
const shareText = encodeURIComponent(
	'Marauders Cheats – ESP & Aimbot tools for Marauders players',
);
---

<section class="home-seo shell" aria-labelledby="home-seo-title">
	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2 id="home-seo-title">Marauders Cheats ESP and Aimbot overview</h2>
		<p>
			{productInfo.summary} This page is the main entry point for players comparing Marauders Cheats
			before purchase. You can review what ESP covers, how Aimbot controls are presented, which package
			lengths are available, and where to find updates or support after checkout.
		</p>
		<p>
			Marauders is a fast extraction-style game where information density matters. Clearer on-screen
			context and predictable aim-assist settings can make package evaluation easier when you are
			deciding between a short monthly license and a longer lifetime option. Use the sections below,
			then open the dedicated product pages for deeper detail.
		</p>

		<div class="home-seo__grid">
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/marauders-esp/">Marauders ESP visibility tools</a></h3>
				<p>
					ESP options focus on readable player and loot awareness so you can understand nearby threats
					and item opportunities without guessing from incomplete screen cues alone.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/marauders-aimbot/">Marauders Aimbot control options</a></h3>
				<p>
					Aimbot settings cover targeting behavior, smoothness, priority choices, and hotkey toggles so
					you can review how assisted aiming is configured before buying.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/features/">Complete Marauders Cheats feature list</a></h3>
				<p>
					The features page groups ESP, Aimbot, and general package tools in one place so you can scan
					capabilities without jumping between marketing blurbs.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article>
				<h3><a href="/support/">Marauders Cheats customer support</a></h3>
				<p>
					Support handles delivery questions, setup help, and order issues. Include your order details
					and a clear description of the problem for faster replies.
				</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2>What Marauders Cheats includes</h2>
		<p>
			Marauders Cheats is sold as a Windows PC software package with ESP and Aimbot feature sets. ESP
			overlays help with player spotting, loot markers, distance readouts, and category toggles. Aimbot
			tools focus on assisted targeting, sensitivity and smoothness controls, target priority, and quick
			on/off hotkeys. General package options include in-client toggles, monthly and lifetime plans,
			update notices, and a support channel for setup or billing questions.
		</p>
		<ul>
			{productInfo.features.esp.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
			{productInfo.features.aimbot.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
			{productInfo.features.general.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
		</ul>
		<p>
			Package pricing is listed on the
			<a href="/pricing/">Marauders Cheats pricing page</a>
			so you can compare duration against budget. Maintenance notes appear on
			<a href="/updates/">product update notices</a>
			whenever a build or compatibility change is published. If you need policy details before buying,
			read the refund, privacy, and terms pages linked in the footer.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="home-seo__panel card-surface">
		<h2>How to evaluate ESP and Aimbot for Marauders</h2>
		<p>
			Start with the combat information you care about most. If raid awareness and loot routing are your
			priority, open the ESP page and confirm which overlay categories match your play style. If assisted
			aiming controls matter more, review Aimbot settings for smoothness, targeting priority, and hotkey
			behavior. Many players check both pages, then use the feature list as a final checklist before
			choosing a monthly or lifetime license.
		</p>
		<p>
			Delivery is digital after payment confirmation. Timing can vary by payment method and order review.
			After purchase, watch the Updates page for maintenance notes tied to Marauders patches, and contact
			support if license delivery or setup needs clarification. Platforms supported today:
			{productInfo.platforms.join(', ')}. Market availability: {siteConfig.market}.
		</p>
		<p>
			This site is designed for clear product research rather than vague claims. Each internal page has a
			focused job: ESP explains visibility tools, Aimbot explains aiming controls, Features summarizes the
			full package, Pricing compares plan lengths, FAQ answers common purchase questions, and Support is
			the contact path when something needs a human reply.
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="home-seo__faq" aria-labelledby="home-faq-title">
		<h2 id="home-faq-title">Frequently asked questions about Marauders Cheats</h2>
		<div class="home-seo__faq-list">
			{
				homeFaqs.map((item) => (
					<details class="home-seo__item">
						<summary>{item.question}</summary>
						<p>{item.answer}</p>
					</details>
				))
			}
		</div>
		<p class="home-seo__more">
			More answers are on the <a href="/faq/">Marauders Cheats FAQ</a>. Policy details are in
			<a href="/refund-policy/">refund policy details</a>,
			<a href="/privacy-policy/">privacy policy details</a>, and
			<a href="/terms/">terms of use</a>.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="home-seo__share" aria-labelledby="share-title">
		<h2 id="share-title">Share Marauders Cheats</h2>
		<p>Pass this page along if someone else is comparing ESP and Aimbot options for Marauders.</p>
		<div class="home-seo__share-row">
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=${shareUrl}&text=${shareText}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on X
			</a>
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=${shareUrl}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on Facebook
			</a>
			<a
				class="share-link"
				href={`https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=${shareUrl}&title=${shareText}`}
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Share on Reddit
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</section>

<style>
	.home-seo {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.card-surface {
		padding: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
		border-radius: var(--radius-card);
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.16);
		background: rgba(26, 22, 38, 0.72);
	}

	.home-seo h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.home-seo p {
		margin: 0.85rem 0 0;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.home-seo ul {
		margin: 1rem 0 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.45rem;
	}

	.home-seo li {
		position: relative;
		padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem 0.55rem 1.85rem;
		border-radius: 0.65rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
		background: rgba(10, 6, 18, 0.35);
		color: #d4cae6;
		font-size: 0.94rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.home-seo li::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.75rem;
		top: 50%;
		width: 0.35rem;
		height: 0.35rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: var(--color-orchid);
		transform: translateY(-50%);
	}

	.home-seo a {
		color: var(--color-orchid);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.home-seo a:hover {
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	.home-seo__grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.85rem;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.home-seo__grid article {
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.9rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(10, 6, 18, 0.35);
	}

	.home-seo__grid h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 750;
	}

	.home-seo__grid p {
		margin-top: 0.45rem;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.home-seo__faq-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.home-seo__item {
		border-radius: 0.85rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(26, 22, 38, 0.65);
		padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
	}

	.home-seo__item summary {
		cursor: pointer;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-ink);
	}

	.home-seo__item p {
		margin-top: 0.65rem;
	}

	.home-seo__more {
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.home-seo__share {
		padding: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
		border-radius: var(--radius-card);
		border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.14);
		background: rgba(18, 16, 26, 0.55);
	}

	.home-seo__share-row {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.share-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 2.5rem;
		padding: 0.55rem 0.95rem;
		border-radius: 0.7rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.25);
		background: rgba(34, 28, 48, 0.85);
		color: var(--color-ink) !important;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition:
			border-color 0.2s ease,
			background 0.2s ease;
	}

	.share-link:hover {
		border-color: rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.5);
		background: rgba(48, 36, 72, 0.9);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.home-seo__grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
